public class Address
extends CompoundItem

Description:

Address as specified in HTML. Typically, This element is rendered in italic typeface and (maybe) indented.

Instructions:

Use this class to add personal information such as address, signature and authorship to your page.

Example: 

// Creates an Address object
Address addr = new Address();
// Add items to Address object
addr.addItem("My Name");
addr.addItem("My Address");
